VE_STR1(Desc_mm_fmadd_pch, "Multiply packed complex numbers in a and b, accumulate to the corresponding complex numbers in c, and store the results in dst.\n Each complex number is composed of two adjacent half-precision (16-bit)\n floating-point elements, which defines the complex number complex = vec.fp16[0] + i * vec.fp16[1].\n\nFOR i := 0 to 3\n\tdst.fp16[2*i+0] := (a.fp16[2*i+0] * b.fp16[2*i+0]) - (a.fp16[2*i+1] * b.fp16[2*i+1]) + c.fp16[2*i+0]\n\tdst.fp16[2*i+1] := (a.fp16[2*i+1] * b.fp16[2*i+0]) + (a.fp16[2*i+0] * b.fp16[2*i+1]) + c.fp16[2*i+1]\nENDFOR\ndst[MAX:128] := 0")
