VE_STR1(Desc_mm_mmask_i32gather_epi32, "Gather 32-bit integers from memory using 32-bit indices. 32-bit elements are loaded from addresses starting at base_addr and offset by each 32-bit element in vindex (each index is scaled by the factor in scale). Gathered elements are merged into dst using writemask k (elements are copied from src when the corresponding mask bit is not set). scale should be 1, 2, 4 or 8.\n\nFOR j := 0 to 3\n\ti := j*32\n\tm := j*32\n\tIF k[j]\n\t\taddr := base_addr + SignExtend64(vindex[m+31:m]) * ZeroExtend64(scale) * 8\n\t\tdst[i+31:i] := MEM[addr+31:addr]\n\tELSE\n\t\tdst[i+31:i] := src[i+31:i]\n\tFI\nENDFOR\ndst[MAX:128] := 0")
